377
00:30:27,359 --> 00:30:28,486
At everything.

378
00:30:29,995 --> 00:30:31,725
You inspire me.

379
00:30:32,831 --> 00:30:33,992
And annoy me.

380
00:30:37,002 --> 00:30:38,334
Small price to pay.

381
00:30:50,549 --> 00:30:52,415
Your mom's gonna be all better.

382
00:31:03,095 --> 00:31:08,033
The lungs sound fine
without any retractions.

383
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:11,969
There's only one way to tell
if the steroids worked well.

384
00:31:12,871 --> 00:31:14,271
Stop bagging.

385
00:31:16,041 --> 00:31:19,307
Hopefully, she can
breathe on her own now.

386
00:31:44,136 --> 00:31:45,195
Bye.

387
00:31:46,271 --> 00:31:48,502
No, no.

388
00:31:53,011 --> 00:31:54,240
We need to sleep.

389
00:31:54,312 --> 00:31:55,940
She is still not finished.

390
00:31:57,249 --> 00:31:59,718
She has to say goodbye.

391
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:02,988
She said goodbye.

392
00:32:03,088 --> 00:32:06,616
It's one of three phrases
