393
00:32:08,126 --> 00:32:11,961
I want her to hold my baby.

394
00:32:17,836 --> 00:32:20,032
She wants you to hold her baby.

395
00:32:43,195 --> 00:32:44,857
Oh.

396
00:32:44,963 --> 00:32:45,963
Oh.

397
00:32:53,338 --> 00:32:55,330
She's so beautiful.

398
00:33:11,389 --> 00:33:12,389
Bastion.

