417
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:38,065
When my court date
came around, I skipped.

418
00:35:38,837 --> 00:35:41,966
And now there's an active
warrant out for me in the States.

419
00:35:43,074 --> 00:35:44,940
That's why I haven't been back.

420
00:35:47,579 --> 00:35:51,380
But what if I got a lawyer,
got this cleared up?

421
00:35:52,717 --> 00:35:56,051
What if I was to start
running toward things?

422
00:35:59,658 --> 00:36:02,184
Would you be interested
in a visitor in San Jose?

423
00:36:10,568 --> 00:36:12,662
There's something
I want to ask you.

424
00:36:34,893 --> 00:36:36,521
I think you should take the job.

425
00:36:37,629 --> 00:36:40,497
Of course she wasn't gonna
poach you without asking me.

426
00:36:45,637 --> 00:36:47,606
I can't speak the language.

427
00:36:47,706 --> 00:36:49,732
I don't know anyone here.

428
00:36:49,808 --> 00:36:52,710
I just started a
relationship with my father.

429
00:36:55,647 --> 00:36:56,910
I'm not ready.

430
00:36:58,717 --> 00:37:00,208
All legit concerns.

431
00:37:01,553 --> 00:37:03,454
But what I didn't hear
was one single reason

432
00:37:03,555 --> 00:37:05,080
you don't want to do this.

433
00:37:06,458 --> 00:37:10,293
You've spent so many years
thinking your heart was a liability.

434
00:37:10,395 --> 00:37:12,523
It made you care too much.

435
00:37:12,597 --> 00:37:14,259
It hurt too much.

436
00:37:18,069 --> 00:37:19,799
But maybe here...

437
00:37:21,806 --> 00:37:24,901
maybe here, caring too
much is exactly what's needed.

438
00:37:50,368 --> 00:37:51,368
Okay.

439
00:37:54,639 --> 00:37:55,800
Aw.

440
00:38:05,984 --> 00:38:07,577
This is about time.

441
00:38:14,392 --> 00:38:16,793
You were far too
good for us, anyway.

442
00:38:17,495 --> 00:38:18,495
Aw.

443
00:38:24,035 --> 00:38:25,401
Proud of you, Dr. Browne.

444
00:38:30,208 --> 00:38:32,040
- Oh.
- Love you.

445
00:38:40,919 --> 00:38:43,013
I'm never quite sure
what you're thinking.

446
00:38:44,622 --> 00:38:45,920
Many things.

447
00:38:48,526 --> 00:38:49,755
That I'm sad.

448
00:38:52,330 --> 00:38:55,732
That this airport is the only one
I've been to without a Cinnabon.

449
00:38:57,569 --> 00:38:59,765
That people need
to move forward.

450
00:39:02,941 --> 00:39:03,941
That...

451
00:39:05,276 --> 00:39:07,939
