458
00:40:21,786 --> 00:40:22,786
No.

459
00:40:25,523 --> 00:40:29,927
But... right now, I know
I won't be sad forever.

460
00:40:29,994 --> 00:40:32,793
And I don't think I would
have gotten there without you.

461
00:40:39,837 --> 00:40:42,602
I want to spend the
rest of my life with you.

462
00:40:45,143 --> 00:40:48,307
I want to spend my
life with you too, Lea.

463
00:40:56,988 --> 00:40:58,479
Will you marry me?

464
00:40:59,857 --> 00:41:02,292
Of course. I love you.

465
00:41:03,294 --> 00:41:04,762
I love you too.

466
00:41:15,873 --> 00:41:18,308
- We are getting married.
- Yeah.

467
00:41:19,177 --> 00:41:20,873
We are getting married!

468
00:41:22,146 --> 00:41:23,978
We are getting married!

469
00:41:25,216 --> 00:41:26,216
Oh, yeah!

470
00:41:26,784 --> 00:41:28,810
- Congratulations!
- Thank you.

471
00:41:30,154 --> 00:41:31,178
Okay.

472
00:41:31,289 --> 00:41:32,780
Oh, yeah.

473
00:41:34,025 --> 00:41:36,517
Okay. I have to tell Claire.

474
00:41:40,031 --> 00:41:41,031
Okay.

475
00:41:49,374 --> 00:41:51,741
Yes. I'm ready.

476
00:42:00,351 --> 00:42:01,182
Scalpel.

477
00:42:01,252 --> 00:42:02,447
Yes, doctor.

478
00:42:06,324 --> 00:42:07,587
Welcome.

479
00:42:09,861 --> 00:42:11,557
Come on.
